array.note: p[j] is the period (time) of the jth product
s[i] is the starting time of the ith stack
e[i] is the ending time of the ith stack
o[i][t] is 1 iff the ith stack is open at time t
ns[t] is the number of open stacks at time t

allDifferent.note: all products are scheduled at different times

group.note: computing the number of open stacks at any time

minimize.note: minimizing the number of stacks that are simultaneously open
